HOW TO MAKE A GOOD MARTINI.

39:43.834 --> 39:47.041
YOU'RE INVITING ME
TO STAY WITH YOU?

39:47.083 --> 39:49.959
UH, WELL, YOU KNOW,
JUST UNTIL

39:50.000 --> 39:52.417
YOU GET THINGS SORTED OUT.

39:52.458 --> 39:56.792
YOU'RE NOT GONNA GET ALL TALKY
ABOUT FEELINGS OR HAIR--
I JUST WANT A MARTINI.

