(Gary Jules &amp; the Group Rules'
"The Old Days Are Gone" playing)

40:03.083 --> 40:06.917
♪ OLD DAYS AND MEMORIES ♪

40:06.959 --> 40:08.667
♪ ARE CALLING YOU NOW ♪

40:08.709 --> 40:10.166
EVENING.

40:10.208 --> 40:11.875
♪ TO GLORIES THAT YOU... ♪

40:11.917 --> 40:14.667
WHAT, YOU'RE NOT GONNA MAKE
SOME WARM-HEARTED COMMENT

40:14.709 --> 40:16.667
ABOUT ME
BEING IN A WHEELCHAIR?

40:16.709 --> 40:18.667
I THOUGHT WE WERE ON A ROLL.

40:18.709 --> 40:21.208
SORRY.

40:21.250 --> 40:23.291
YOU OKAY?

40:23.333 --> 40:25.041
♪ THE OLD DAYS ARE GONE,
HALLELUJAH ♪

40:25.083 --> 40:27.542
UM...

40:29.083 --> 40:31.208
♪ OUT IN THE COUNTRY ♪

