AND I TRIED TO FORCE HER
TO HAVE AN AB-ABORTION.

40:40.917 --> 40:45.333
AND I DON'T BELIEVE IN ABORTION.

40:45.375 --> 40:47.917
(stammers) I'VE GONE
OVER THE EDGE...

40:47.959 --> 40:50.959
(crying) AND I DON'T KNOW
WHAT TO DO.

40:51.000 --> 40:52.500
♪ HALLELUJAH ♪

40:52.542 --> 40:54.458
(crying)

40:54.500 --> 41:00.375
♪ WAY OVER THE WATER ♪

41:00.417 --> 41:04.041
♪ TOMORROW IS COMING TO YOU ♪

41:04.083 --> 41:06.041
(sobbing)

41:06.083 --> 41:09.583
♪ IN THE OLD DAYS YOU HELD IT ♪

41:09.625 --> 41:13.041
♪ IN THE PALM OF YOUR HAND ♪

41:13.083 --> 41:15.792
♪ THE OLD DAYS ARE GONE,
HALLELUJAH ♪

41:15.834 --> 41:19.083
THIS... THIS NEVER HAPPENED.
(sniffles)

41:19.125 --> 41:22.083
DAMN RIGHT,
IT NEVER HAPPENED.

41:22.125 --> 41:25.291
♪♪♪

41:26.834 --> 41:28.959
I DON'T KNOW
IF WHAT HAPPENED T--

41:29.000 --> 41:33.542
OR WHAT DIDN'T HAPPEN TODAY
WAS...

41:33.583 --> 41:36.000
THE BEST THING OR...

41:36.041 --> 41:37.917
OR A MISTAKE.

41:37.959 --> 41:39.041
(sighs)

41:39.083 --> 41:40.750
I DON'T KNOW.

41:40.792 --> 41:43.041
HOW CAN YOU KNOW?

41:43.083 --> 41:45.542
I MEAN,
YOU MAKE A CHOICE.

41:45.583 --> 41:48.291
YOU DO WHAT YOU THINK
IS RIGHT AT THE TIME.

41:48.333 --> 41:50.125
I MEAN, THE PLAN IS--

41:50.166 --> 41:54.208
MEET A GUY, FALL IN LOVE,
HAVE A FAMILY.

41:54.250 --> 41:57.041
BUT YOU HAVE TO BE SPECIFIC.

41:57.083 --> 42:00.792
BE OLDER THAN 15,
MEET THE RIGHT GUY,

42:00.834 --> 42:02.959
STAY IN LOVE.

42:03.000 --> 42:04.542
STAY IN LOVE.

42:04.583 --> 42:05.834
MM.

42:05.875 --> 42:08.625
I KNEW I FORGOT SOMETHING.
HMM.

